schools.name: Cobalt Institute Of Math And Science Academy

data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!! This Spacious 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home comes with a BONUS ROOM, turn into a 4th bedroom, office, gym or whatever you need.  This home not only has a cozy Den with a fireplace but also features a formal living room and formal dining room with high ceilings for a touch of elegance. Master Bedroom or Primary Bedroom has plenty room and presenting a massive walk-in-closet that will not disappoint. The Front has great curb appeal with the rock landscape for low maintenance yard.  Side to side patio coverage promoting partially low maintenance aluminum and a massive shed included for your storage needs.  Convenient alley in the back allows for entrance through the back fence. All this centrally located near schools, stores and parks. Big bonus it's close to the freeway making it commuter friendly.
